quran[16{c,v,t}:
38,1,"s, qasam hai nasiyaat bharay quran ki"
38,2,"balkay yahi log, jinhon ne maan-ne se inkaar kya hai, sakht taqqabur aur zid mein mubtala hain"
38,3,"inn se pehlay hum aisi kitni hi qomon ko halaak kar chuke hain ( aur jab unn ki shamat aayi hai ) to woh cheekh utthay hain, magar woh waqt bachney ka nahi hota"
38,4,"inn logon ko is baat par bara taajjub howa ke aik darane wala khud aِnhi mein se agaya munkareen kehnay lagey ke"" yeh sahit hai, sakht jhoota hai"
38,5,"kya iss ne saaray khudaon ki jagah bas aik hi khuda bana dala? yeh to barri ajeeb baat hai """
38,6,"aur sardaran -e- qoum yeh kehte hue nikal gay ke"" chalo aur datay raho apne mabodon ki ibadat par yeh baat to kisi aur hi gharz se kahi ja rahi hai"
38,7,yeh baat hum ne zamana qareeb ki millat mein kisi se nahi suni yeh kuch nahi hai magar aik mann gharat baat
38,8,"kya hamaray darmain bas yahishakhs reh gaya tha jis par Allah ka zikar nazil kar diya gaya ?"" asal baat yeh hai ke yeh mere"" zikar"" par shak kar rahay hain, aur yeh saari baatein is liye kar rahay hain ke unhon ne mere azaab ka maza chakkha nahi hai"
38,9,kya tairay dataa aur ghalib parvar-digaar ki rehmat ke khazanay inn ke qabzay mein hain ?
38,10,kya yeh aasman o zameen aur un ke darmain ki cheezon ke maalik hain? acha to yeh aalam asbaab ki bulandiyon par charh kar dekhen !
38,11,yeh to jathonmein se aik chhota sa jatha hai jo isi jagah shikast khanay wala hai
38,12,"inn se pehlay Nooh ki qoum, aur Aad , aur mekhon wala firaon"
38,13,"aur smod, aur qoum Loot , aur aikah walay jhutla chuke hain jthe woh thay"
38,14,un mein se har aik ne Rasolo-n ko jhtlaya aur meri uqobat ka faisla is par chaspan ho kar raha
38,15,yeh log bhi bas aik dhamakay ke muntazir hain jis ke baad koi dosra dhamaka nah hoga
38,16,"aur yeh kehte hain ke ae hamaray rab, yom ul hisaab se pehlay hi hamara hissa hamein jaldi se de day"
